import React from 'react';
import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom';
import {
  Box,
  Typography,
  Button,
  Paper,
  Grid,
} from '@mui/material';

function Home() {
  const navigate = useNavigate();

  return (
    <Box
      sx={{
        display: 'flex',
        flexDirection: 'column',
        alignItems: 'center',
        gap: 4,
        py: { xs: 4, md: 8 },
      }}
    >
      <Typography
        variant="h1"
        component="h1"
        align="center"
        sx={{
          mb: 2,
          color: 'primary.main',
          fontWeight: 'bold',
        }}
      >
        CyberQuiz
      </Typography>

      <Typography
        variant="h5"
        component="h2"
        align="center"
        sx={{
          mb: 4,
          maxWidth: 'sm',
          mx: 'auto',
        }}
      >
        Test your cybersecurity knowledge and learn how to protect yourself online
      </Typography>

      <Paper
        elevation={3}
        sx={{
          p: { xs: 2, sm: 4 },
          width: '100%',
          maxWidth: 'md',
          borderRadius: 2,
        }}
      >
        <Grid container spacing={3} direction="column" alignItems="center">
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <Typography variant="h6" align="center" gutterBottom>
              Ready to start your cybersecurity journey?
            </Typography>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <Button
              variant="contained"
              size="large"
              onClick={() => navigate('/quiz')}
              sx={{
                px: 4,
                py: 1.5,
                fontSize: '1.2rem',
              }}
            >
              Start Quiz
            </Button>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Paper>

      <Box
        sx={{
          mt: 4,
          p: 3,
          backgroundColor: 'background.paper',
          borderRadius: 2,
          width: '100%',
          maxWidth: 'md',
        }}
      >
        <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom align="center">
          Features
        </Typography>
        <Grid container spacing={3} sx={{ mt: 1 }}>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
            <Typography variant="subtitle1" align="center">
              üéØ Interactive Questions
            </Typography>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
            <Typography variant="subtitle1" align="center">
              üèÜ Score Tracking
            </Typography>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
            <Typography variant="subtitle1" align="center">
              üì± Mobile Friendly
            </Typography>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default Home;
